cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.SD

The paper describes the development of a graphical user interface for collecting human-robot dialogue data, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), robotics (cs.RO), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and software development (cs.SD). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.HC and cs.RO, followed by cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.SD.
